file.name: readOnlyWriteOnly.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Users
paths:
  /users/required:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
  /users/optional:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserOptional"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserOptional"
  /users/hal:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/hal+json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/hal+json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
  /users/nested:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Nested"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Nested"

  /users/usersArray:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/UsersArray"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/UsersArray"
  /users/OneOf:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/OneOf"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/OneOf"
  /users/AnyOf:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/AnyOf"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/AnyOf"
  /users/AllOf:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/AllOf"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/AllOf"

components:
  schemas:
    UserRequired:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - email
        - password
      additionalProperties: false
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
        email:
          type: string
        password:
          type: string
          writeOnly: true
    UserOptional:
      type: object
      additionalProperties: false
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
        email:
          type: string
        password:
          type: string
          writeOnly: true
    Nested:
      type: object
      required:
        - user
        - lastLogin
      properties:
        user:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
        lastLogin:
          type: number
          format: date-time
          readOnly: true
    UsersArray:
      type: array
      items:
        type: object
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
    OneOf:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
        - type: object
          required:
            - additionalOneOfField
          properties:
            additionalOneOfField:
              type: string
    AnyOf:
      anyOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
        - type: object
          required:
            - additionalOneOfField
          properties:
            additionalOneOfField:
              type: string
    AllOf:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/UserRequired"
        - type: object
          required:
            - additionalOneOfField
          properties:
            additionalOneOfField:
              type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/users/hal": post: requestBody: contents: unsupported content types: [application/hal+json]
